{"tid":1810361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時見d正女好想中出，但又唔想生仔","createTime":"2020-01-03T20:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:04:12.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43b822b0a09c9ccc144bda86b32950089772a76e","tid":1810361,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:31:41.000Z","msg":"諗返自己呢世經歷<br />\n其實好感慨<br />\n好唔開心<br />\n痛苦都形容唔到咁多年感受<br />\n而家只係麻木左自己<br />\n或者時間沖淡左<br />\n講真<br />\n自己應該都得唔到<br />\n自己心底裏想要既女<br />\n但就算係平行時空<br />\n就算真係中出到<br />\n自己都未必接受生仔呢樣野<br />\n一黎生仔就等於你唔再做仔<br />\n二黎好困身<br />\n個細路又未必想做人<br />\n個世界又咁多人<br />\n又咁撚熱<br />\n自己都叫做有幸見過雪<br />\n但下一代好難講<br />\n仲有人一生真係好多野買<br />\n又衫褲鞋襪又盛<br />\n同埋始終<br />\n自己潛意識始終想永遠做細路<br />\n而唔係做細路既老豆"},{"pid":"78f3bc4667abb246031bf6170151b3158d78af83","tid":1810361,"uid":56999,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yefBsm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyefBsm1.jpg&h=b225f3dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4be335f34b8f239ab2acdcce559b06bde507c61","tid":1810361,"uid":50060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:39:29.000Z","msg":"Vasectomy"},{"pid":"674614ec62502aa862f8d4d7d280ed6513b2b396","tid":1810361,"uid":77985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:41:29.000Z","msg":"事後、避孕丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58241f1caf9a304687fd0bb6b825531fa274f5b9","tid":1810361,"uid":342202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4be335f34b8f239ab2acdcce559b06bde507c61","tid":1810361,"uid":50060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:39:29.000Z","msg":"Vasectomy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T20:41:55.000Z","msg":"呢個答案簡直完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5599a939c86bd010b2f08ae325f4084d9bd2cc91","tid":1810361,"uid":229834,"like":1,"dislike":